The torrent that I posted was regarding The Super Best Friends episode from Season 5 of South Park. An account I had previously, subliminalz, posted this torrent years ago here on ThePirateBay. It mysteriously vanished, along with the account. 

This South Park episode has been taken down time and time again, from ComedyCentral.com, to other torrent sites, and even on this site. The reasoning for this was that it portrays &quot;Muhammad&quot;, an Islamic figure, and according to Islam you may not portray his likeness anywhere at anytime for any reason. 

That's Islam. I am not Islamic. Most of you are not Islamic. Your rules do not apply to me and never will. I will continue to post this AND seed it as long as it needs it.

May this video live on FOREVER in the name of freedom of censorship.
